nativefiledialog-extended
------------------------------------------
A small C library with that portably invokes native file open, folder select
and file save dialogs. Write dialog code once and have it pop up native dialogs
on all supported platforms. Avoid linking large dependencies like wxWidgets and
Qt.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.3-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.64.6-1
  libgtk3_0-3.24.43-1
  libnfd-devel-1.2.0-1bl1
  libnfd1-1.2.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.2.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.42-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-2
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-2
  libglib2.0-devel-2.64.6-1
  libgtk3-devel-3.24.43-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/btzy/nativefiledialog-extended

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/btzy/nativefiledialog-extended/archive/refs/tags/v1.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack nativefiledialog-extended-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./nativefiledialog-extended-1.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/nativefiledialog-extended-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/nativefiledialog-extended-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libnfd1-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libnfd-devel-1.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(nativefiledialog-extended)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/nativefiledialog-extended.README
  /usr/share/doc/nativefiledialog-extended/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/nativefiledialog-extended/README.md

(libnfd1)
  /usr/bin/cygnfd-1.dll

(libnfd-devel)
  /usr/include/nfd.h
  /usr/include/nfd.hpp
  /usr/include/nfd_glfw3.h
  /usr/include/nfd_sdl2.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/nfd/nfd-config-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/nfd/nfd-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/libnfd.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/nativefiledialog-extended.pc

